{
  "chapter": 17,
  "chapter_summary": "第十七回\"断肠时节\"讲述南宫平、梅吟雪、风漫天与七哥四人中毒后在海上漂流。七哥因毒性最先发作而自尽解脱，梅吟雪毒发时被风漫天点穴昏睡，南宫平发现自己体内\"阴魂\"与\"阳魄\"两种剧毒互相克制竟安然无恙。船至诸神岛，梅吟雪被麻衣老人救活，发现南宫平灵位以为他已死，痛不欲生。风漫天违背\"四绝戒令\"带梅吟雪去见被关在洞窟中的南宫平，南宫平因发誓不再理梅吟雪而闭目不语。梅吟雪含恨离去，南宫平在洞窟中度过百日，背诵了大量武功秘笈。出洞后进入诸神之殿，见到岛主白发老人，得知岛上将野兽变为人类、研究各种奇技异术的秘密。最终南宫平在石窟中与恩师龙布诗重逢，二人约定在狂欢之日寻找逃离的机会。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_man_tian",
      "speaker_name": "风漫天",
      "listener": "char_qi_ge",
      "text": "你要先去了么？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_ge",
      "speaker_name": "七哥",
      "listener": "char_feng_man_tian",
      "text": "我要先去了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_man_tian",
      "speaker_name": "风漫天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好好，这……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_yin_xue",
      "speaker_name": "梅吟雪",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "好了，我也要先去了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_yin_xue",
      "speaker_name": "梅吟雪",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "我生怕你比我先去，那痛苦我真的难以忍受，现在……我……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "南宫平",
      "listener": "char_mei_yin_xue",
      "text": "吟雪，吟雪……你等等我……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "南宫平",
      "listener": "char_feng_man_tian",
      "text": "风老前辈，求求你将我也……",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "南宫平",
      "listener": "char_feng_man_tian",
      "text": "风老前辈，你怎样了？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_man_tian",
      "speaker_name": "风漫天",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "我……",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_man_tian",
      "speaker_name": "风漫天",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "谢……",
      "tone": "感激",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "南宫平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "苍天呀苍天，我怎地还不死呢？",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": "char_feng_man_tian",
      "text": "风漫天，你回来了么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "麻衣老人",
      "listener": "char_mei_yin_xue",
      "text": "你醒来了？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 127,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_yin_xue",
      "speaker_name": "梅吟雪",
      "listener": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "text": "我醒来了？……我难道没有死么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_yin_xue",
      "speaker_name": "梅吟雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他的尸身在哪里？我……要去和他死在一起！",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "麻衣老人",
      "listener": "char_mei_yin_xue",
      "text": "你可哭够了么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_yin_xue",
      "speaker_name": "梅吟雪",
      "listener": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "text": "南宫平，你……你知道他……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "麻衣老人",
      "listener": "char_mei_yin_xue",
      "text": "你若是未曾哭够，大可以再哭一场，你若是已经哭够，我便带你上船，别的话你也不必问了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_yin_xue",
      "speaker_name": "梅吟雪",
      "listener": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "text": "你不愿回答，我自会去寻，也毋庸阁下费心带我上船。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "麻衣老人",
      "listener": "char_mei_yin_xue",
      "text": "你走不得！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_yin_xue",
      "speaker_name": "梅吟雪",
      "listener": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "text": "我要走便走，谁说我走不得？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "麻衣老人",
      "listener": "char_mei_yin_xue",
      "text": "你若是在此岛上要走一步，便砍断你的双足。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "麻衣老人",
      "listener": "char_mei_yin_xue",
      "text": "片时之内，你若不上船远离此地，莫怪老夫无礼了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_yin_xue",
      "speaker_name": "梅吟雪",
      "listener": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "text": "这么大年纪的男人，还要苦苦纠缠着一个年轻的女孩子，不害臊么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "麻衣老人",
      "listener": "char_mei_yin_xue",
      "text": "好刁猾的女子……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "麻衣老人",
      "listener": "char_mei_yin_xue",
      "text": "回去！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_yin_xue",
      "speaker_name": "梅吟雪",
      "listener": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "text": "看你道貌岸然，仿佛年高德重，想不到你却是个凶险的小人！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "麻衣老人",
      "listener": "char_mei_yin_xue",
      "text": "你说什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_yin_xue",
      "speaker_name": "梅吟雪",
      "listener": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "text": "若非凶险小人，为什么毫无仁厚之心，如此欺负我一个可怜的未亡人……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_yin_xue",
      "speaker_name": "梅吟雪",
      "listener": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "text": "他人已死了，你为什么还不让我看一看他的尸身，难道你……真……的……这么……狠心……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_mao_shou_ren",
      "speaker_name": "金毛兽人",
      "listener": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "text": "主人有何吩咐？",
      "tone": "恭敬",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 197,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "麻衣老人",
      "listener": "char_jin_mao_shou_ren",
      "text": "货物可曾全都卸下？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_mao_shou_ren",
      "speaker_name": "金毛兽人",
      "listener": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "text": "还未曾！",
      "tone": "恭敬",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "麻衣老人",
      "listener": "char_jin_mao_shou_ren",
      "text": "退下！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "麻衣老人",
      "listener": "char_mei_yin_xue",
      "text": "货一卸完，便将你送上船去，我以灵药救你一命，已非易事，你应该满足了！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "麻衣老人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "人呢？我就不信她能插翅飞出此厅！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 233,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "text": "她若未插翅飞出此厅，难道是隐身不见了么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "麻衣老人",
      "listener": "char_feng_man_tian",
      "text": "诸神岛上，百余年来，素无女子的足迹，这女子既是你带来的，还需你带出此地。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_man_tian",
      "speaker_name": "风漫天",
      "listener": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "text": "慢走，她此刻人影不见，怎知不是你放走的。",
      "tone": "怀疑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "麻衣老人",
      "listener": "char_feng_man_tian",
      "text": "她就在你挡住的桌子下面，哼哼！方才人门时这桌子不住摇动，你当我未曾看到么？你虽然赶去挡住，却已来不及了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_yin_xue",
      "speaker_name": "梅吟雪",
      "listener": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "text": "他没有死么？此刻他在哪里？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "麻衣老人",
      "listener": "char_mei_yin_xue",
      "text": "不错，他确是未死，只是你今生再也休想见着他了！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_yin_xue",
      "speaker_name": "梅吟雪",
      "listener": "char_feng_man_tian",
      "text": "真的么？风老前辈，他说的是真的么？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_man_tian",
      "speaker_name": "风漫天",
      "listener": "char_mei_yin_xue",
      "text": "不错！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_yin_xue",
      "speaker_name": "梅吟雪",
      "listener": "char_feng_man_tian",
      "text": "他是我的夫婿，我为什么不能见他？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_yin_xue",
      "speaker_name": "梅吟雪",
      "listener": "char_feng_man_tian",
      "text": "风老前辈，我此刻对你说的话，你切莫误会，我绝非以救命恩人的身份对你说话，因为我有心要救的根本不是你，我只是站在一个曾经同船共渡的人那种地位向你说话。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_yin_xue",
      "speaker_name": "梅吟雪",
      "listener": "char_feng_man_tian",
      "text": "我一个弱女子，又敌不过你们的武功，你们说什么，我自然无法反抗，我虽然不能活着见他，就请在我死后，将我的尸身带去见他。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "麻衣老人",
      "listener": "char_mei_yin_xue",
      "text": "你想死在这里么？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_yin_xue",
      "speaker_name": "梅吟雪",
      "listener": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "text": "此刻我别的事不能做主，要死总是可以的吧。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "麻衣老人",
      "listener": "char_mei_yin_xue",
      "text": "你死了之后，我一样也是要将你的尸身送到船上，你死上十次，也是见不着他。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_yin_xue",
      "speaker_name": "梅吟雪",
      "listener": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "text": "呀！你老人家真是位大英雄大丈夫……",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_yin_xue",
      "speaker_name": "梅吟雪",
      "listener": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "text": "好好，你们两位都是大英雄……",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_man_tian",
      "speaker_name": "风漫天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "跟我来！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_yin_xue",
      "speaker_name": "梅吟雪",
      "listener": "char_feng_man_tian",
      "text": "哪里去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "麻衣老人",
      "listener": "char_feng_man_tian",
      "text": "哪里去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_man_tian",
      "speaker_name": "风漫天",
      "listener": "char_mei_yin_xue",
      "text": "我带你去见他！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_yin_xue",
      "speaker_name": "梅吟雪",
      "listener": "char_feng_man_tian",
      "text": "真……真的？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "麻衣老人",
      "listener": "char_feng_man_tian",
      "text": "不是真的！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "麻衣老人",
      "listener": "char_feng_man_tian",
      "text": "绝情，绝欲，绝名，绝利！诸神岛代代相传的'四绝戒令'，阁下难道已忘记了么？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_man_tian",
      "speaker_name": "风漫天",
      "listener": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "text": "未曾忘记。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "麻衣老人",
      "listener": "char_feng_man_tian",
      "text": "那么阁下为何……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_man_tian",
      "speaker_name": "风漫天",
      "listener": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "text": "风某四十年前，心中无名利色欲之念，但这情之一字，却是再也绝不掉的，此番我带她前去，一切后果，自有我一人担当，不劳阁下费心。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "麻衣老人",
      "listener": "char_feng_man_tian",
      "text": "你既要自寻苦恼，我也只得由你……只怕你见着他后，更要伤心一些。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "麻衣老人",
      "listener": "char_feng_man_tian",
      "text": "风兄，你如此做，你难道忘了……",
      "tone": "警告",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_man_tian",
      "speaker_name": "风漫天",
      "listener": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "text": "忘了什么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "麻衣老人",
      "listener": "char_feng_man_tian",
      "text": "你难道忘了此岛的禁例，以你两人之力，便想和诸神岛的禁例对抗，岂非做梦？若是惊动了大殿上的长老，到那时你两人求生不得，求死也不能，不但害了自己，也害了别人了。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_yin_xue",
      "speaker_name": "梅吟雪",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "小平，你不愿意和我死在一起么？我们一起死了，也远比在这里受罪好得多，你若张开眼睛看我一眼，我死了也心甘情愿，你……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_yin_xue",
      "speaker_name": "梅吟雪",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "人生最大难便是一死，你那誓言真有那么严重么？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "麻衣老人",
      "listener": "char_mei_yin_xue",
      "text": "你一心想死，别人却不愿死哩。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_yin_xue",
      "speaker_name": "梅吟雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好！我走！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "麻衣老人",
      "listener": "char_mei_yin_xue",
      "text": "随我来！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "南宫平",
      "listener": "char_mei_yin_xue",
      "text": "吟雪，我……我对不起你……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_man_tian",
      "speaker_name": "风漫天",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "但愿她能了解你我的苦衷……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "南宫平",
      "listener": "char_feng_man_tian",
      "text": "我知道她必将恨我一生，我也绝不怪她，但是……但是我多么愿意她知道我这么对她，是为了什么！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_man_tian",
      "speaker_name": "风漫天",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "她永远也不会知道的……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "麻衣老人",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "恭喜阁下，正式成为诸神岛上一员。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "麻衣老人",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "自今日起，阁下便可换一个居处了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "麻衣老人",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "这便是你的居处。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "麻衣老人",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "这便是你的名字，到了时候，我自会带你入殿，但未到时候，你却不得走离此间一步。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 429
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "南宫平",
      "listener": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "text": "哼！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "麻衣老人",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "你可有什么话要问我么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "南宫平",
      "listener": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "text": "没有！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "麻衣老人",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "好！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "麻衣老人",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "跟我来！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "你来了么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "一直走，莫回头！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "这里！上来！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "南宫平",
      "listener": "char_bai_fa_lao_ren",
      "text": "在下南宫平……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 516,
      "line_end": 516
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fa_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白发老人",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "止水，你名叫止水，记得么？你一入此岛，便与世俗红尘完全脱离，必须将以前所有的一切俱都忘去，知道么？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "南宫平",
      "listener": "char_bai_fa_lao_ren",
      "text": "世俗红尘中的声名荣誉，在下早已忘了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 528
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fa_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白发老人",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "好好。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 530
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fa_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白发老人",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "就凭此话，该喝一杯！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 532
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fa_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白发老人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "酒来！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 532,
      "line_end": 532
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fa_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白发老人",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "你以前有曾见过这样的人类么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 540
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "南宫平",
      "listener": "char_bai_fa_lao_ren",
      "text": "在下还未不幸到那种程度！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fa_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白发老人",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "是了，你自然未曾见过，你可知道，这哪里是人，它根本就是只野兽……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 550
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "南宫平",
      "listener": "char_bai_fa_lao_ren",
      "text": "如此说来，那'七哥'以及那……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 550
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fa_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白发老人",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "那些也全都是野兽，老夫一生致力'华陀神术'，费了数十年心血，才将十余只野兽创造成人……",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 552,
      "line_end": 552
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "南宫平",
      "listener": "char_bai_fa_lao_ren",
      "text": "但……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 554,
      "line_end": 554
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fa_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白发老人",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "百十年前，武林曾有一人，能将人类肢体随意移动，他能将你的手掌移植到头上，鼻子移植到手上，而且让它在那里生长，于是他便造成了不少妖物，他自己在世人眼中，也变成了妖物。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 556,
      "line_end": 558
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fa_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白发老人",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "但他这种技巧，与老夫相比，却仍是望尘莫及，只因他这不过只是将皮肤甚至骨骼移植，造成畸形之人，而老夫却是将人类的生命，赋与野兽，想来纵然华陀复生，也未见得能有老夫今日的成就！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 558,
      "line_end": 560
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fa_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白发老人",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "我将那些人的俗尘全都洗净后，便要他们来研究这些工作……那些洞窟，便是他们的工作之处，你且瞑目想上一想，这些幻想实现之后，这功业岂非足以流传百世。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 662,
      "line_end": 664
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fa_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白发老人",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "今日我话已说得太多，耽误了不少工作，你进入此间后，言语行动，已无限制，但每年却只能见着天光一次，此刻你不妨去四下看看，然后随意选个石室住下，等到明日，我再唤你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 668,
      "line_end": 670
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 690,
      "line_end": 692
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "龙布诗",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "我正在研究将空气变为食物，空气……你可知道空气是什么！空气便是存在于天地间的一种……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 698,
      "line_end": 700
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "龙布诗",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "平儿，可……是……你么……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 700,
      "line_end": 700
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "南宫平",
      "listener": "char_long_bu_shi",
      "text": "师傅！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 704,
      "line_end": 706
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "南宫平",
      "listener": "char_long_bu_shi",
      "text": "师傅，你老人家怎地到了这里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 714,
      "line_end": 714
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_bu_shi",
      "speaker_name": "龙布诗",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "平儿，你怎会到了这里？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 716,
      "line_end": 716
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "南宫平",
      "listener": "char_long_bu_shi",
      "text": "徒儿还有一事要上禀你老人家，徒儿已成婚了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 718,
      "line_end": 718
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_bu_shi",
      "speaker_name": "龙布诗",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "那女子是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 722,
      "line_end": 722
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "南宫平",
      "listener": "char_long_bu_shi",
      "text": "梅吟雪！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 724,
      "line_end": 724
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_bu_shi",
      "speaker_name": "龙布诗",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "人道红颜多薄命，这女子却真是薄命人中最薄命的人，我只望她能有个安静幸福的暮年弥补她一生中所遭受的不幸与冤枉，哪知……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 726,
      "line_end": 726
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "南宫平",
      "listener": "char_long_bu_shi",
      "text": "徒儿曾见到那'天帝留宾'四字，还以为你老人家已到了另外一处神秘的地方，不知那日在华山之巅，究竟发生了什么事？师傅你老人家又怎会到了这里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 730,
      "line_end": 732
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_bu_shi",
      "speaker_name": "龙布诗",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "华山之巅，华山之巅……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 734,
      "line_end": 734
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_bu_shi",
      "speaker_name": "龙布诗",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "四十年前，我初次听到'诸神殿'三字的时候，便对此地充满了幻想，今日我已真的到了此地，却对此地失望得很，但……唉！却已迟了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 738,
      "line_end": 740
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "南宫平",
      "listener": "char_long_bu_shi",
      "text": "师傅，那'空气'是否便是充沛于天地间的一种无形气体，你老人家却又能用什么方法将之变为食物？空气真能变为食物，那么天下岂非再无饥民了。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 742,
      "line_end": 744
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_bu_shi",
      "speaker_name": "龙布诗",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "平儿，你可知道这岛上之人大多全是疯子，不是疯子的人，经过那数百日的幽禁，洗尘，过着那坟墓中死人一般的生活，只怕也差不多了……",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 746,
      "line_end": 746
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_bu_shi",
      "speaker_name": "龙布诗",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "这些疯子中最大的疯子，便是那大头岛主。在此岛上，在他统辖之下，谁的心智清醒，谁便是疯子，为师到了这里，见到这般情况，实在无法整日面对着那些行尸走肉一般的老人，宁愿独自思索，便对那岛主大发荒谬的言论！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 750,
      "line_end": 754
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "南宫平",
      "listener": "char_long_bu_shi",
      "text": "什么言论？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 756,
      "line_end": 756
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_bu_shi",
      "speaker_name": "龙布诗",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "为师对那岛主说，花草树木，之所以生长繁荣，便是因为吸入了空气中的养分，人们若是将风露中的一种神秘物质提出凝固，做成食物，那当真不知要节省多少人力、物力，而且天地间满是风露，取之不尽，用之不竭，亦不知可救活多少饥民。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 758,
      "line_end": 760
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_bu_shi",
      "speaker_name": "龙布诗",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "那岛主听了为师这番言论，果然大是兴奋，大表钦服，认为是空前未有的伟大计划，是以不经手续，便将为师请来这里，一切东西，都任凭为师取用，是以我这里才有许多美酒。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 762,
      "line_end": 764
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_bu_shi",
      "speaker_name": "龙布诗",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "平儿，为师虽然日卧醉乡，但却始终未曾失望灰心，时时在伺机而动，那岛主若再唤你，你便可求他将你派来此地与为师一起研究这'神秘的食物'，约莫再过数月，便是一个机会，那时我师徒能在一起，机会便更大了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 768,
      "line_end": 770
    }
  ],
